OL,3,CNew Chief Minister candidates explain
OL,4,Chow they will tackle Jersey's key
OL,5,Cissues
OL,7,FFollowing a vote of no confidence in
OL,8,Fon Wednesday 17 January, three
OL,9,Fcandidates are preparing for the
OL,10,Felection on Thursday 25 January where
OL,11,Fmembers of the States will decide who
OL,12,Fwill replace her.
OL,14,FThe three candidates are Deputy Ian
OL,15,FGorst, a former Chief Minister and
OL,16,FTreasury Minister in the previous
OL,17,Fgovernment, who positions himself as
OL,18,Fcentre-right.
