OL,7,FDeputy Lyndon Farnham is a former
OL,8,FDeputy Chief Minister, who was first
OL,9,Felected to the States in 1999 and is
OL,10,Fcentre-right.
OL,12,FDeputy Sam Mezec is the leader of
OL,13,FReform Jersey and a former Housing
OL,14,FMinister.
OL,16,FIn their final hours in the run-up to
OL,17,Fthe election, the three deputies have
OL,18,Fshared their views on the issues that
OL,19,Fmatter to the island.
