OL,7,FOn plans for a new hospital, Deputy
OL,8,FGorst says: "I think it is a great
OL,9,Fplan, I think there is a great
OL,10,Fopportunity, I think we can afford
OL,11,Fwhat is being proposed and we should
OL,12,Fjust stop bickering and arguing and
OL,13,Fget on with it."
