OL,7,FDeputy Mezek says, "I don't think 10
OL,8,Fyears since we started this project
OL,9,Fand the #100 million plus wasted on
OL,10,Fit, that we start from scratch and go
OL,11,Fthrough that exercise again, I think
OL,12,Fwe need to stick to the plans we have
OL,13,Fgot and just try to make them work as
OL,14,Fbest as possible."
OL,16,FThey each added how they would tackle
OL,17,Fthe housing and cost of living crises
OL,18,Fin Jersey.
