OL,4,Chow they will tackle Jersey's key
OL,5,Cissues
OL,7,FDeputy Sam Mezec says: "I have a
OL,8,Fcomprehensive housing crisis action
OL,9,Fplan that on the very first day of my
OL,10,Fleadership I would put to an emergency
OL,11,Ftask force and start implementing.
OL,13,F"This means doing things like reducing
OL,14,Frent control, it means expanding on
OL,15,Fschemes to support first-time buyers.
OL,17,F"It is an absolute crisis for Jersey,
OL,18,Fand we must resolve it, if we don't
OL,19,Fget to grips with it then frankly
OL,20,FJersey is finished."
