OL,7,FHe added, "I am the only candidate
OL,8,Fthat knows that the status quo is
OL,9,Fbroken and I've got a record that
OL,10,Fshows I am not afraid to stand up to
OL,11,Fvested interest."
OL,13,FDeputy Ian Gorst says: "There is a
OL,14,Ffeeling in the assembly and across the
OL,15,Fisland that the government hasn't been
OL,16,Flistening, so I want to work with the
OL,17,Ffood banks to understand fully with
OL,18,Fthem what is happening, what islanders
OL,19,Fare experiencing and then develop
OL,20,Ftogether policy intervention that will
OL,21,Fmake a real difference."
