OL,7,FLyndon Farnham explains: "We need to
OL,8,Ffind financial support, 100% loan
OL,9,Fschemes with much longer repayment
OL,10,Fperiods. Deposit saving schemes and
OL,11,Fshared equity in other areas we should
OL,12,Fbe promoting.
OL,14,FHe adds: "If we start making a
OL,15,Fdifference to some of those things, we
OL,16,Fcan start making a difference"
